enumerationMembers.label: OrderCancelled
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing cancellation of an order.

enumerationMembers.label: OrderDelivered
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing successful delivery of an order.

enumerationMembers.label: OrderInTransit
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing that an order is in transit.

enumerationMembers.label: OrderPaymentDue
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing that payment is due on an order.

enumerationMembers.label: OrderPickupAvailable
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing availability of an order for pickup.

enumerationMembers.label: OrderProblem
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing that there is a problem with the order.

enumerationMembers.label: OrderProcessing
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing that an order is being processed.

enumerationMembers.label: OrderReturned
enumerationMembers.comment: OrderStatus representing that an order has been returned.
